cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI 

The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically with inferring detailed human body shape from a single photograph. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and 3D modeling, which suggests the categories cs.GR (Computer Graphics), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques, which could place it in the category cs.LG (Machine Learning).
